snippet: Australia beat England by 150 runs in the third Ashes test in Perth to take an insurmountable 3-0 lead in the five-match series.
abstract: Australian cricket team beats England in the third Ashes test in Perth, taking insurmountable 3-0 lead in the five-match series.
